Subject: drm/i915: Simplify intel_set_cdclk_{pre,post}_plane_update() calling
 convention
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 5604e9ceaed59956c5027832c9f09d48ab3126cb
